---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';
import ProgressBar from '../components/ProgressBar.astro';
import OSTabs from '../components/OSTabs.astro';
import StepCard from '../components/StepCard.astro';
import CodeBlock from '../components/CodeBlock.astro';
import Celebration from '../components/Celebration.astro';
import AdUnit from '../components/AdUnit.astro';
import LangSwitcher from '../components/LangSwitcher.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';

// Steps 0–7 — step 8 is the celebration screen, not a trackable step
const steps = [
  { id: 0, title: 'Prerequisitos', icon: '✅' },
  { id: 1, title: 'Instalar Claude Code', icon: '📦' },
  { id: 2, title: 'Configurar PATH', icon: '🔧' },
  { id: 3, title: 'API Key', icon: '🔑' },
  { id: 4, title: 'Primera verificación', icon: '🚀' },
  { id: 5, title: 'Configuración esencial', icon: '⚙️' },
  { id: 6, title: 'Shortcuts & Tips', icon: '💡' },
  { id: 7, title: 'Directivas & .gitignore', icon: '📁' },
];
---

<Layout>
  <div class="app-layout">
    <Sidebar steps={steps} />

    <main class="main-content">
      <ProgressBar total={steps.length} />

      <header class="page-header">
        <div class="page-header-top">
          <h1 data-i18n="headerTitle">Claude Code — Guía de instalación</h1>
          <div class="page-header-lang-mobile">
            <LangSwitcher />
          </div>
        </div>
        <p data-i18n="headerSubtitle">
          Seguí este paso a paso para instalar, configurar y empezar a usar Claude Code,
          la CLI oficial de Anthropic para trabajar con IA desde tu terminal.
        </p>
      </header>

      <OSTabs />

      <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <!-- STEP 0: PREREQUISITES                                           -->
      <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <StepCard stepId={0} title="Prerequisitos" icon="✅">

        <!-- ── ESPAÑOL ── -->
        <div class="lang-block" data-lang="es">
          <p>Claude Code requiere <strong>Node.js versión 18 o superior</strong>. Verificá tu versión actual:</p>
          <CodeBlock code="node --version" lang="bash" />
          <p>Si el comando falla o la versión es menor a 18, instalá Node.js según tu sistema:</p>
          <h3>Instalar Node.js</h3>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <p>Opción 1 — Usando <strong>winget</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="winget install OpenJS.NodeJS.LTS" lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell" />
            <p>Opción 2 — Descargá el instalador desde <a href="https://nodejs.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nodejs.org</a> y ejecutá el archivo <code>.msi</code>.</p>
            <div class="info-box"><span>💡</span><span>Durante la instalación marcá la opción <strong>"Add to PATH"</strong>.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="macos">
            <p>Con <strong>Homebrew</strong> (recomendado):</p>
            <CodeBlock code="brew install node" lang="bash" os="macos" />
            <p>O con <strong>nvm</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.1/install.sh | bash\nnvm install --lts`} lang="bash" os="macos" label="nvm" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="linux">
            <p>Con <strong>nvm</strong> (recomendado):</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.1/install.sh | bash\nsource ~/.bashrc\nnvm install --lts`} lang="bash" os="linux" label="nvm" />
            <p>O con apt (Ubuntu/Debian):</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_lts.x | sudo -E bash -\nsudo apt-get install -y nodejs`} lang="bash" os="linux" label="apt" />
          </div>
          <h3>Verificar instalación</h3>
          <CodeBlock code={`node --version\nnpm --version`} lang="bash" />
          <div class="success-box"><span>✓</span><span>Si ambos devuelven un número de versión, Node.js está listo.</span></div>
        </div>

        <!-- ── ENGLISH ── -->
        <div class="lang-block" data-lang="en">
          <p>Claude Code requires <strong>Node.js version 18 or higher</strong>. Check your current version:</p>
          <CodeBlock code="node --version" lang="bash" />
          <p>If the command fails or the version is below 18, install Node.js for your OS:</p>
          <h3>Install Node.js</h3>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <p>Option 1 — Using <strong>winget</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="winget install OpenJS.NodeJS.LTS" lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell" />
            <p>Option 2 — Download the installer from <a href="https://nodejs.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nodejs.org</a> and run the <code>.msi</code> file.</p>
            <div class="info-box"><span>💡</span><span>During install, check <strong>"Add to PATH"</strong>.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="macos">
            <p>With <strong>Homebrew</strong> (recommended):</p>
            <CodeBlock code="brew install node" lang="bash" os="macos" />
            <p>Or with <strong>nvm</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.1/install.sh | bash\nnvm install --lts`} lang="bash" os="macos" label="nvm" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="linux">
            <p>With <strong>nvm</strong> (recommended):</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.1/install.sh | bash\nsource ~/.bashrc\nnvm install --lts`} lang="bash" os="linux" label="nvm" />
            <p>Or with apt (Ubuntu/Debian):</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_lts.x | sudo -E bash -\nsudo apt-get install -y nodejs`} lang="bash" os="linux" label="apt" />
          </div>
          <h3>Verify installation</h3>
          <CodeBlock code={`node --version\nnpm --version`} lang="bash" />
          <div class="success-box"><span>✓</span><span>If both commands return a version number, Node.js is ready.</span></div>
        </div>

        <!-- ── PORTUGUÊS ── -->
        <div class="lang-block" data-lang="pt">
          <p>O Claude Code requer <strong>Node.js versão 18 ou superior</strong>. Verifique sua versão atual:</p>
          <CodeBlock code="node --version" lang="bash" />
          <p>Se o comando falhar ou a versão for menor que 18, instale o Node.js:</p>
          <h3>Instalar Node.js</h3>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <p>Opção 1 — Usando <strong>winget</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="winget install OpenJS.NodeJS.LTS" lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell" />
            <p>Opção 2 — Baixe o instalador em <a href="https://nodejs.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nodejs.org</a> e execute o arquivo <code>.msi</code>.</p>
            <div class="info-box"><span>💡</span><span>Durante a instalação, marque <strong>"Add to PATH"</strong>.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="macos">
            <p>Com <strong>Homebrew</strong> (recomendado):</p>
            <CodeBlock code="brew install node" lang="bash" os="macos" />
            <p>Ou com <strong>nvm</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.1/install.sh | bash\nnvm install --lts`} lang="bash" os="macos" label="nvm" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="linux">
            <p>Com <strong>nvm</strong> (recomendado):</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.40.1/install.sh | bash\nsource ~/.bashrc\nnvm install --lts`} lang="bash" os="linux" label="nvm" />
            <p>Ou com apt (Ubuntu/Debian):</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_lts.x | sudo -E bash -\nsudo apt-get install -y nodejs`} lang="bash" os="linux" label="apt" />
          </div>
          <h3>Verificar instalação</h3>
          <CodeBlock code={`node --version\nnpm --version`} lang="bash" />
          <div class="success-box"><span>✓</span><span>Se ambos retornarem um número de versão, o Node.js está pronto.</span></div>
        </div>
      </StepCard>

      <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <!-- STEP 1: INSTALL CLAUDE CODE                                     -->
      <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <StepCard stepId={1} title="Instalar Claude Code" icon="📦">

        <!-- ── ESPAÑOL ── -->
        <div class="lang-block" data-lang="es">
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <h3>Paso previo — habilitar scripts en PowerShell</h3>
            <p>Por defecto Windows bloquea la ejecución de scripts <code>.ps1</code>. Habilitá los scripts para tu usuario:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser`} lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell" />
            <div class="info-box"><span>💡</span><span>Esto solo afecta tu usuario, no el sistema. Es el ajuste recomendado para desarrollo.</span></div>
            <h3>Instalar Claude Code</h3>
            <p>Ahora ejecutá el instalador oficial:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`irm https://claude.ai/install.ps1 | iex`} lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell — instalador oficial" />
            <div class="info-box"><span>💡</span><span>El script descarga e instala <code>claude.exe</code> en <code>$HOME\.local\bin\</code> y actualiza el PATH automáticamente.</span></div>
            <p>Alternativa — via npm (requiere Node.js ≥18):</p>
            <CodeBlock code="npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code" lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell — npm" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="macos">
            <p>Instalá globalmente via <strong>npm</strong> desde la Terminal:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code" lang="bash" os="macos" label="Terminal" />
            <div class="warning-box"><span>⚠️</span><span>Si recibís error de permisos, <strong>no uses sudo</strong>. Usá nvm o corregí los permisos de npm.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="linux">
            <p>Instalá globalmente via <strong>npm</strong> desde la terminal:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code" lang="bash" os="linux" label="Terminal" />
            <div class="warning-box"><span>⚠️</span><span>Si recibís error de permisos, <strong>no uses sudo</strong>. Usá nvm o configurá npm para instalar en tu home.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-box"><span>⏳</span><span>La instalación puede tardar unos segundos.</span></div>
          <h3>Verificar instalación</h3>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="macos">
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="bash" os="macos" label="Terminal" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="linux">
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="bash" os="linux" label="Terminal" />
          </div>
          <p>Deberías ver algo como <code>claude/1.x.x</code>.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- ── ENGLISH ── -->
        <div class="lang-block" data-lang="en">
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <h3>First — enable PowerShell scripts</h3>
            <p>Windows blocks <code>.ps1</code> scripts by default. Enable them for your user:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser`} lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell" />
            <div class="info-box"><span>💡</span><span>This only affects your user, not the system. It's the recommended setting for development.</span></div>
            <h3>Install Claude Code</h3>
            <p>Now run the official installer:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`irm https://claude.ai/install.ps1 | iex`} lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell — official installer" />
            <div class="info-box"><span>💡</span><span>The script downloads and installs <code>claude.exe</code> in <code>$HOME\.local\bin\</code> and updates PATH automatically.</span></div>
            <p>Alternative — via npm (requires Node.js ≥18):</p>
            <CodeBlock code="npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code" lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell — npm" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="macos">
            <p>Install globally via <strong>npm</strong> from Terminal:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code" lang="bash" os="macos" label="Terminal" />
            <div class="warning-box"><span>⚠️</span><span>If you get a permissions error, <strong>don't use sudo</strong>. Use nvm or fix npm permissions.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="linux">
            <p>Install globally via <strong>npm</strong> from the terminal:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code" lang="bash" os="linux" label="Terminal" />
            <div class="warning-box"><span>⚠️</span><span>If you get a permissions error, <strong>don't use sudo</strong>. Use nvm or configure npm to install in your home directory.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-box"><span>⏳</span><span>Installation may take a few seconds.</span></div>
          <h3>Verify installation</h3>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="macos">
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="bash" os="macos" label="Terminal" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="linux">
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="bash" os="linux" label="Terminal" />
          </div>
          <p>You should see something like <code>claude/1.x.x</code>.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- ── PORTUGUÊS ── -->
        <div class="lang-block" data-lang="pt">
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <h3>Primeiro — habilitar scripts no PowerShell</h3>
            <p>O Windows bloqueia scripts <code>.ps1</code> por padrão. Habilite para o seu usuário:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser`} lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell" />
            <div class="info-box"><span>💡</span><span>Isso afeta apenas o seu usuário, não o sistema. É o ajuste recomendado para desenvolvimento.</span></div>
            <h3>Instalar Claude Code</h3>
            <p>Agora execute o instalador oficial:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`irm https://claude.ai/install.ps1 | iex`} lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell — instalador oficial" />
            <div class="info-box"><span>💡</span><span>O script baixa e instala <code>claude.exe</code> em <code>$HOME\.local\bin\</code> e atualiza o PATH automaticamente.</span></div>
            <p>Alternativa — via npm (requer Node.js ≥18):</p>
            <CodeBlock code="npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code" lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell — npm" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="macos">
            <p>Instale globalmente via <strong>npm</strong> pelo Terminal:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code" lang="bash" os="macos" label="Terminal" />
            <div class="warning-box"><span>⚠️</span><span>Se receber erro de permissão, <strong>não use sudo</strong>. Use nvm ou corrija as permissões do npm.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="linux">
            <p>Instale globalmente via <strong>npm</strong> pelo terminal:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code" lang="bash" os="linux" label="Terminal" />
            <div class="warning-box"><span>⚠️</span><span>Se receber erro de permissão, <strong>não use sudo</strong>. Use nvm ou configure o npm para instalar no seu diretório home.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="info-box"><span>⏳</span><span>A instalação pode levar alguns segundos.</span></div>
          <h3>Verificar instalação</h3>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="macos">
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="bash" os="macos" label="Terminal" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="linux">
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="bash" os="linux" label="Terminal" />
          </div>
          <p>Você deve ver algo como <code>claude/1.x.x</code>.</p>
        </div>
      </StepCard>

      <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <!-- STEP 2: PATH CONFIGURATION                                      -->
      <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <StepCard stepId={2} title="Configurar PATH" icon="🔧">

        <!-- ── ESPAÑOL ── -->
        <div class="lang-block" data-lang="es">
          <p>Para que el comando <code>claude</code> esté disponible en cualquier terminal, el directorio del binario debe estar en tu <strong>PATH</strong>.</p>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <h3>Si usaste el instalador oficial</h3>
            <p>El instalador actualiza el PATH automáticamente. Verificá abriendo una <strong>nueva terminal</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="powershell" os="windows" />
            <p>Si no funciona, agregá manualmente <code>%USERPROFILE%\.local\bin</code> al PATH:</p>
            <h3>Opción 1 — PowerShell</h3>
            <CodeBlock code={`$path = "$env:USERPROFILE\\.local\\bin"\n[Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable("Path", $env:Path + ";$path", [EnvironmentVariableTarget]::User)\nWrite-Host "PATH actualizado. Reiniciá la terminal."`} lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell" />
            <h3>Opción 2 — GUI del sistema</h3>
            <ol style="padding-left: 1.25rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.9rem;">
              <li>Presioná <kbd>Win + R</kbd>, escribí <code>sysdm.cpl</code> y Enter.</li>
              <li><strong>Opciones avanzadas</strong> → <strong>Variables de entorno</strong>.</li>
              <li>En <strong>Variables de usuario</strong> → <strong>Path</strong> → doble clic.</li>
              <li>Clic en <strong>Nuevo</strong> → pegá <code>%USERPROFILE%\.local\bin</code>.</li>
              <li>Aceptar y reiniciar la terminal.</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="warning-box"><span>⚠️</span><span>Reiniciá la terminal para que los cambios tengan efecto.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="macos">
            <h3>Agregar al shell profile</h3>
            <p>Para <strong>Zsh</strong> (shell por defecto en macOS moderno):</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`echo 'export PATH="$(npm config get prefix)/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.zshrc\nsource ~/.zshrc`} lang="bash" os="macos" label="zsh" />
            <p>Para <strong>Bash</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`echo 'export PATH="$(npm config get prefix)/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.bash_profile\nsource ~/.bash_profile`} lang="bash" os="macos" label="bash" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="linux">
            <h3>Agregar al shell profile</h3>
            <p>Para <strong>Bash</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`echo 'export PATH="$(npm config get prefix)/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.bashrc\nsource ~/.bashrc`} lang="bash" os="linux" label="bash" />
            <p>Para <strong>Zsh</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`echo 'export PATH="$(npm config get prefix)/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.zshrc\nsource ~/.zshrc`} lang="bash" os="linux" label="zsh" />
          </div>
          <div class="success-box"><span>✓</span><span>Si <code>claude --version</code> responde correctamente, el PATH está listo.</span></div>
        </div>

        <!-- ── ENGLISH ── -->
        <div class="lang-block" data-lang="en">
          <p>For the <code>claude</code> command to work in any terminal, its directory must be in your <strong>PATH</strong>.</p>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <h3>If you used the official installer</h3>
            <p>The installer updates PATH automatically. Verify by opening a <strong>new terminal</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="powershell" os="windows" />
            <p>If it fails, manually add <code>%USERPROFILE%\.local\bin</code> to PATH:</p>
            <h3>Option 1 — PowerShell</h3>
            <CodeBlock code={`$path = "$env:USERPROFILE\\.local\\bin"\n[Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable("Path", $env:Path + ";$path", [EnvironmentVariableTarget]::User)\nWrite-Host "PATH updated. Restart your terminal."`} lang="powershell" os="windows" label="PowerShell" />
            <h3>Option 2 — System GUI</h3>
            <ol style="padding-left: 1.25rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.9rem;">
              <li>Press <kbd>Win + R</kbd>, type <code>sysdm.cpl</code>, press Enter.</li>
              <li><strong>Advanced</strong> → <strong>Environment Variables</strong>.</li>
              <li>Under <strong>User variables</strong> → <strong>Path</strong> → double click.</li>
              <li>Click <strong>New</strong> → paste <code>%USERPROFILE%\.local\bin</code>.</li>
              <li>Accept and restart your terminal.</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="warning-box"><span>⚠️</span><span>Restart your terminal for changes to take effect.</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="macos">
            <h3>Add to shell profile</h3>
            <p>For <strong>Zsh</strong> (macOS default):</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`echo 'export PATH="$(npm config get prefix)/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.zshrc\nsource ~/.zshrc`} lang="bash" os="macos" label="zsh" />
            <p>For <strong>Bash</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`echo 'export PATH="$(npm config get prefix)/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.bash_profile\nsource ~/.bash_profile`} lang="bash" os="macos" label="bash" />
          </div>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="linux">
            <h3>Add to shell profile</h3>
            <p>For <strong>Bash</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`echo 'export PATH="$(npm config get prefix)/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.bashrc\nsource ~/.bashrc`} lang="bash" os="linux" label="bash" />
            <p>For <strong>Zsh</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code={`echo 'export PATH="$(npm config get prefix)/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.zshrc\nsource ~/.zshrc`} lang="bash" os="linux" label="zsh" />
          </div>
          <div class="success-box"><span>✓</span><span>If <code>claude --version</code> responds correctly, your PATH is configured.</span></div>
        </div>

        <!-- ── PORTUGUÊS ── -->
        <div class="lang-block" data-lang="pt">
          <p>Para que o comando <code>claude</code> funcione em qualquer terminal, o diretório do binário deve estar no seu <strong>PATH</strong>.</p>
          <div class="os-content" data-os="windows">
            <h3>Se usou o instalador oficial</h3>
            <p>O instalador atualiza o PATH automaticamente. Verifique abrindo um <strong>novo terminal</strong>:</p>
            <CodeBlock code="claude --version" lang="powershell" os="windows" />
            <p>Se falhar, adicione manualmente <code>%USERPROFILE%\.local\bin</code> ao PATH:</p>
            <h3>Opção 1 — PowerShell</h3>
